OL,5, A documentary about a Welsh sheep      
OL,6, farmer has beaten over 7,000 films to  
OL,7, earn a place at the Tribeca Film       
OL,8, Festival in New York.                  
OL,10,FHeart Valley follows a day in the life 
OL,11,Fof Wilf Davies, 73, from Cellan, near  
OL,12,FLampeter in Ceredigion.                
OL,14,FDirector Christian Cargill pitched the 
OL,15,Ffilm to Mr Davies after reading a      
OL,16,Ffeature in the Guardian about his life 
OL,17,Fand devotion to his flock of 70 sheep. 
OL,19,FMr Cargill said the farmer was         
OL,20,F"humbled" the film had been selected.  
